This directory contains some miscellaneous tutorial examples.

The file test.rb is an example to show how to use jruby (jruby.codehaus.org) with jReality.  To run this example with the JOGL backend enabled:
1) download jruby (jruby.codehaus.org) 
2) setenv CLASSPATH  to include the jarfiles jReality.jar, jtem-beans.jar, and jogl.jar
3) setenv JAVA_LIBRARY_PATH to include the native libraries for jogl.
4) run "jruby test.rb"
